<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Danielle Lloyd has unveiled her 10 day body transformation. </p>

<p>Following her recent holiday to Turkey, where she admitted she had drank and eaten 'whatever she wanted', the CBB star underwent a health overhaul. </p>

<p>Taking to Instagram on Thursday, she shared six images showing her before and after images while posing in lingerie. </p>

<p>Changing shape: Danielle Lloyd has unveiled her 10 day body transformation</p>

<p>Danielle was plugging her Ketone diet in the post, as she admitted she has slimmed down thanks to her new drink and no exercise. </p>

<p>Sharing a lengthy caption, she penned: 'So 10 days ago I decided to do one of my 10 day challenges. I’d been on a few holidays and drank and eaten what I wanted...</p>

<p>'I’ve lost 3lb but as you can see my body shape and bloat has definitely changed along with my energy and focus I just feel so much better in myself...</p>

<p>'This is no alcohol for the 10 days but no exercise either I just couldn’t get the gym with the kids being off school...</p>

<p>Slimmed down: Following her recent holiday to Turkey, where she admitted she had drank and eaten 'whatever she wanted', the CBB star underwent a health overhaul</p>

<p>'It’s 2 simple drinks a day with no diet. I did limit my carbs intake but had them each day and even had <?php echo e('@'); ?>halotopuk and chocolate (not everyday)</p>

<p>Am going to continue on with another 10 day challenge starting from today and will post the results from them also. #ketones #ketonesforfuel #10daychallenge #missketones'.</p>

<p>Danielle recently had to quarantine for 14 days after heading to Ibiza with her partner after the government pulled its air bridge with Spain following a spike in COVID-19 cases. </p>

